        <item>
            <title>海关破获 Party Room 唱 K 侵权　使用串流技术提供侵权歌曲</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/party-room-copyright/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=party-room-copyright</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/party-room-copyright/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 15:02:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[侵权]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡拉 OK]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[海关]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1253330</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>除了在正规的卡拉 OK 可以唱 K 之外，也有一些号称 Party Room（派对房间）或者食肆会提供相关服务，不过其中也有违法提供侵权歌曲，也就是没有正规授权的地方。最近海关就采取行动，首次破获侵权的 Party Room。<br /><span id="more-1253330"></span></p><p>据报导指，海关在 7 月 2 日至 25 日在全港各区采取代号「喜鹊」的执法行动，突击搜查 31 间派对房间及 1 间火锅店，其店主涉嫌向顾客提供侵权卡拉 OK 歌曲。行动中拘捕 18 人﹐今次也是海关首度破获 Party Room，海关指这些店铺，透过数据中心以串流技术提供侵权歌曲，增加了海关的追查难度。</p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/p2024072600520_photo-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253332" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/p2024072600520_photo-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/p2024072600520_photo-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>执法人员在行动中查获大量涉嫌侵权的设备，包括 39 台歌曲播放机、4 台电子游戏机，以及其他影音和网络设备，总价值约 110 万港元。海关字播放机内储存了超过 180 万首疑似侵权歌曲。海关版权及商标科技罪案调查组高级调查主任梁文聪表示，不法份子在铜锣湾一个商业大厦设置数据中心，以串流技术，经路由器和互联网将歌曲传送到区内 4 间 Party Room 内的电视，而顾客就用手机扫瞄二维码点歌。</p><p>而 Party Room 在社交平台或网页声称，持有特许或牌照容许的影音播放服务，「合法」提供影音影片，但事实上有关牌照早已失效，令顾客在不知情下观看侵权节目，也属于涉嫌违反《商品说明条例》。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202407/26/P2024072600520.htm">政府新闻处</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/party-room-copyright/hottopic/spotlight/">海关破获 Party Room 唱 K 侵权　使用串流技术提供侵权歌曲</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/party-room-copyright/hottopic/spotlight/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>SMS 骗案假扮惠康积分换领网站　加 $4.7 换领气炸锅呃信用卡资料</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/wellcome-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wellcome-scam</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/wellcome-scam/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:00:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[惠康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[骗案]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1253288</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">冒认电讯商和官方机构的骗案经常出现，最近就有网民在讨论区上分享自己收到骗徒假扮成大型连锁超级市场惠康的诈骗短讯，更被骗走个人资料和信用卡资料，呼吁各位提防受骗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253289 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2003-342x580.jpg" alt="" width="342" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2003-342x580.jpg 342w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2003.jpg 531w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 342px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253290 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2004-341x580.jpg" alt="" width="341" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2004-341x580.jpg 341w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2004.jpg 529w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 341px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253291 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2005-340x580.jpg" alt="" width="340" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2005-340x580.jpg 340w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2005.jpg 528w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 340px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253292 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2006-338x580.jpg" alt="" width="338" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2006-338x580.jpg 338w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2006.jpg 525w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 338px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253293 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2007-339x580.jpg" alt="" width="339" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2007-339x580.jpg 339w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2007.jpg 527w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 339px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/3746486">LIHKG 讨论区</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">这位网民指自己收到了假惠康的短讯，指自己的账户积分将会于当日到期，提醒他点击附上的连结进入网站兑换礼品。他形容骗徒制作的假惠康积分换领网站非常逼真，顶端又有惠康的商标而不虞有诈。他又指网站内可换领的礼品非常吸引，其中包括电竞耳机、智能手表、电动牙刷和小米气炸锅等，全部都只需要足够的积分再加 $4.7 即可换领。他一时被优惠吸引，按网站指示输入了自己的个人资料和信用卡资料，事后才惊觉自己受骗并在讨论区上寻求协助和警世。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253294 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2008-281x580.jpg" alt="" width="281" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2008-281x580.jpg 281w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2008.jpg 437w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 281px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/3746486">LIHKG 讨论区</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">这个帖文一发布随即引起热议，但普遍网民的反应都是不理解为何仍有人会因为这些小便宜而受骗。警方守网者指过去一周已接获 37 宗诈骗短讯相关的举报，其中最常被伪冒的是 CSL、SmarTone、HKeToll、Mannings 和 CMHK。香港资讯科技商会荣誉会长方保侨认为大部分银行都不愿意负责因受害人疏忽所造成的损失，而且骗徒会用受害人的信用卡购买难以追踪的点数卡，受害人很大机会难以追回损失。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.stheadline.com/society/3366977/%E5%81%87%E6%83%A0%E5%BA%B7SMS%E7%A9%8D%E5%88%86%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88-%E5%8A%A047%E5%8F%AF%E6%8F%9B%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%B0%A3%E7%82%B8%E9%8D%8B-%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E5%91%BB%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%96%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%96-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%80%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%87%E7%A9%BF%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80">星岛</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/3746486">LIHKG 讨论区</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/apple-chinascam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国诈骗集团假 iPhone 换真机     Apple 十年被骗超过 9600 万港元</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/hkdoublescam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">警方接获 6 宗网上「二次诈骗」案，苦主被骗后再损失多一次「律师费」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/deepfake-scam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">英国驻港公司堕 Deepfake 骗局，误认骗徒为上司被骗 400 万元</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/wellcome-scam/tech-secure/">SMS 骗案假扮惠康积分换领网站　加 $4.7 换领气炸锅呃信用卡资料</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
